	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />- A few things check if the PPU is "rendering", like mapper IRQs and 2004h. I don't know if the "rendering" translates as "BG or sprites enabled AND scanline between 21 and 260 (or 0 and 239)", or only screen ON. I wonder if the HBlank period is taken into account...

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


